# Project Guidelines

## Application Constants
- All hardcoded values, dimensions, labels, and animation durations should be defined in `[AppConstants.kt](mdc:app/src/main/java/com/technitedminds/wallet/presentation/constants/AppConstants.kt)`.
- Before adding new constants, check if a suitable one already exists.
- Group constants logically within nested objects for clarity.

## Utilities and Extensions
- Before writing new utility functions or extensions, check the existing files to avoid duplication.
- **General Extensions**: `[Extensions.kt](mdc:app/src/main/java/com/technitedminds/wallet/utils/Extensions.kt)` contains common extensions for `Activity`, `View`, and `Context`.
- **Navigation Extensions**: `[NavigationExtensions.kt](mdc:app/src/main/java/com/technitedminds/wallet/presentation/navigation/NavigationExtensions.kt)` provides helper functions for `NavController` to handle navigation patterns.
- **Animation Utilities**: `[AnimationUtils.kt](mdc:app/src/main/java/com/technitedminds/wallet/presentation/components/animation/AnimationUtils.kt)` contains reusable animation modifiers and functions for Jetpack Compose.
- **Category Utilities**: `[CategoryUtils.kt](mdc:app/src/main/java/com/technitedminds/wallet/presentation/components/common/CategoryUtils.kt)` provides functions for resolving category names and icons.